  - m_Id: 441432821760
    m_Localized: Athus, an unconquered dungeon deep within a remote mountain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7361887621120
    m_Localized: Right in front of the dungeon lies a guild established to support
      adventurers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7454170697728
    m_Localized: Sigh... At this rate, how could I ever face the past Guild Masters...?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7635096195072
    m_Localized: Just as Sherry Athus, the current manager of the guild, let out
      a deep sigh...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7637562445824
    m_Localized: (RUMBLE...!)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7639613460480
    m_Localized: A hot spring suddenly erupted in the guild's front yard!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7641760944128
    m_Localized: I-it's a miracle! With this hot spring, we can definitely draw people
      back!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7674396823552
    m_Localized: Sherry Athus immediately fired off a business proposal to headquarters
      to remodel the guild into a 'Hot Spring Inn'.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7676976320512
    m_Localized: I've been waiting for you! You must be the one dispatched from headquarters.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7679610343424
    m_Localized: I'm Sherry Athus, the manager of this guild and a descendant of
      the Athus family. I can't wait to work with you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7681250316288
    m_Localized: We don't have much time, so let's get right to it. First, shall
      we tap the [Build] button to construct our first 'onsen' facility?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7686904238080
    m_Localized: Perfect! To think I'd get to see a hot spring in person that I've
      only ever seen on paper...!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7688015728640
    m_Localized: But we can't just leave it sitting there by itself, right? Please
      build a 'road' leading to the 'onsen' so our guests can get around comfortably.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7688955252736
    m_Localized: Great, the basic preparations for welcoming our guests are complete!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7689882193920
    m_Localized: Don't worry if you accidentally place a facility in the wrong spot.
      You can always move or demolish it by long-pressing it. I'll handle all the
      pesky paperwork!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7690813329408
    m_Localized: Oh, and did you check the [Upgrade] button in the facility info?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7691715104768
    m_Localized: Once the guild gathers enough resources, you can upgrade your facilities.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7692713349120
    m_Localized: The better the facilities, the higher the guild's revenue and reputation
      will soar! Let's make upgrading everything our first goal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
